SECTION 1. Section one of Republic Act Numbered Five thousand two hundred five is hereby amended to read as follows:

"SECTION 1. The WAPCO classification and pay plan shall be adjusted to the following salaries of certain positions in the Veterans Memorial Hospital, which are hereby fixed as follows:

"(a) Director, fifteen thousand pesos,

per annum

;

"(b) Assistant Director, fourteen thousand five hundred pesos

per annum

;

"(c) Chief of Professional Staff, fourteen thousand Pesos,

per annum

;

"(d) Medical Specialist III, thirteen thousand five hundred pesos

per annum

;

"(e) Medical Specialist II, twelve thousand pesos,

per annum

;

''(f) Hospital Department Head, Chief of Service and Chief of Division (non-medical), twelve thousand pesos,

per annum

;

"(o) Medical Specialist I, eleven thousand pesos,

per annum

;

"(h) Senior Resident Physician and Clinic Supervisor nine thousand pesos,

per annum

;

"(i) Resident Physician, Clinic Physician and Junior Physician, seven thousand pesos,

per annum

;

"Those serving on part-time basis shall receive one-half of the corresponding salaries mentioned herein."
